title: Wolfenstein 3D - All 6 Episodes
description:
Ladies and Gentlemen I present to you the CD COLLECTORS EDITION of
WOLFENSTEIN 3D

TESTED
Windows XP / Vista INSTALL READY

CONTAINS ALL 6 EPISODES

GAME DESCRIPTION:
In Wolfenstein 3D, the player is an American soldier (Polish descent) named BJ Blazkowicz attempting to escape from the titular Nazi stronghold; there are many armed guards, as well as attack dogs. The building has a number of hidden rooms containing various treasures, food supplies, and medical kits, as well as three different guns and ammunition.

PACKAGE CONTAINS:
Install Files
Install READ ME
Walkthrough
